detaileddescription.para: A benchmark that evaluates the file skipping capabilities in the Spark data source for Iceberg.
This class uses a dataset with a flat schema, where the records are clustered according to the column used in the filter predicate.
The performance is compared to the built-in file source in Spark.

To run this benchmark for spark-3.3: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.3 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-3.3_2.12:jmh -PjmhIncludeRegex=IcebergSourceFlatParquetDataFilterBenchmark -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/iceberg-source-flat-parquet-data-filter-benchmark-result.txt
